= ChamaleonProject -- Warning =

We are working on another base and another encryption for the server.
Do not create another branch for this, everything will be in the main branch.
All errors please report them promptly.

===============================

ChamaleonProject is a Rift game server emulator. It is derived
from SiennaCore and is based on the code of that project.

Updates in the downloads:
ChameleonWeb_23_06_2011 RevBeta_1.zip
ChameleonDB_02_07_2011 RevBeta_2.zip

SQL files and WEB files can be found in the downloads of GitHub Repo. Files
to update your database from an older revision/version can be found in the
Tools/DatabaseUpdater directory. And there you can find other helpful tools.